sentences.english: The national government of Nanjing implements the separation of the five branches system.
sentences.chinese: 南京國民政府實行五權分立的五院體制。

sentences.english: The commission assigned the academy the task of building these missiles.

sentences.english: The academy scheduled R&D on the missile to be completed before 1962.

sentences.english: In 1957, Qian was appointed president of the five branches.
sentences.chinese: 1957年，錢學森被任命爲五院院長。
